<%- include('partials/header') %>
<div class="static-page">
    <h1><%= title %></h1>
    
    <div class="help-intro">
        <p>Welcome to our Help Center! Find answers to common questions and get the support you need.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="help-sections">
        <div class="help-section">
            <h2>üõçÔ∏è Orders & Shopping</h2>
            <div class="help-items">
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>How do I place an order?</h3>
                    <p>Browse our products, select your size and color, add items to your cart, and proceed to checkout. You can complete your purchase as a guest or create an account for faster future checkouts.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>Can I modify or cancel my order?</h3>
                    <p>Orders can be modified or cancelled within 1 hour of placement. After this time, your order enters our fulfillment process and cannot be changed.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
                    <p>We accept all major credit cards (Visa, MasterCard, American Express), PayPal, Apple Pay, and Google Pay.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="help-section">
            <h2>üì¶ Shipping & Delivery</h2>
            <div class="help-items">
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>How long does shipping take?</h3>
                    <p>Standard shipping takes 3-7 business days. Express shipping (1-3 business days) and overnight shipping options are also available at checkout.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>Do you ship internationally?</h3>
                    <p>Yes! We ship to over 100 countries worldwide. International shipping times vary by destination (7-21 business days).</p>
                </div>
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>How can I track my order?</h3>
                    <p>Once your order ships, you'll receive a tracking number via email. You can also track your order by visiting our <a href="/track-order">Order Tracking</a> page.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="help-section">
            <h2>‚Ü©Ô∏è Returns & Exchanges</h2>
            <div class="help-items">
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>What is your return policy?</h3>
                    <p>We offer free returns within 30 days of purchase. Items must be unworn, unwashed, and in original condition with tags attached.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>How do I return an item?</h3>
                    <p>Log into your account, go to your order history, and select "Return Items." Print the prepaid return label and drop off at any authorized shipping location.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>Can I exchange for a different size?</h3>
                    <p>Yes! You can exchange for a different size or color within 30 days. The exchange process is the same as returns - just specify your preferred replacement item.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="help-section">
            <h2>üìè Sizing & Fit</h2>
            <div class="help-items">
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>How do I find my size?</h3>
                    <p>Use our size guide available on each product page. Measure yourself and compare to our size chart for the best fit. When in doubt, size up!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>What if my item doesn't fit?</h3>
                    <p>No worries! We offer free exchanges and returns. Our <a href="/fit-guarantee">Fit Guarantee</a> ensures you'll love how your gear fits.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>Do you offer wide or narrow width options?</h3>
                    <p>Yes, many of our shoes are available in wide (W) and narrow (N) widths. Look for width options on the product page.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="help-section">
            <h2>üë§ Account & Profile</h2>
            <div class="help-items">
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>How do I create an account?</h3>
                    <p>Click "Sign Up" in the top right corner of any page. You'll need to provide your email address and create a password.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>I forgot my password</h3>
                    <p>Click "Forgot Password" on the sign-in page. Enter your email address and we'll send you a reset link.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>How do I update my account information?</h3>
                    <p>Sign in to your account and go to "My Profile" to update your personal information, shipping addresses, and payment methods.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="help-section">
            <h2>üí∞ Discounts & Promotions</h2>
            <div class="help-items">
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>Do you offer student discounts?</h3>
                    <p>Yes! Students get 10% off with valid student ID verification. Visit our <a href="/student-discount">Student Discount</a> page to learn more.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>Military discount available?</h3>
                    <p>We're proud to offer 15% off for active military, veterans, and their families. Check out our <a href="/military-discount">Military Discount</a> program.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="help-item">
                    <h3>How do I use a promo code?</h3>
                    <p>Enter your promo code in the "Promo Code" field during checkout. The discount will be applied to your order total.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-contact">
        <h2>Still Need Help?</h2>
        <p>Can't find what you're looking for? Our customer service team is here to help!</p>
        <div class="contact-options">
            <div class="contact-option">
                <h3>üìß Email Support</h3>
                <p>Send us an email at <strong>support@runningstore.com</strong></p>
                <p>We typically respond within 24 hours</p>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-option">
                <h3>üìû Phone Support</h3>
                <p>Call us at <strong>1-800-RUN-HELP</strong></p>
                <p>Monday-Friday: 8AM-8PM EST<br>Saturday-Sunday: 9AM-6PM EST</p>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-option">
                <h3>üí¨ Live Chat</h3>
                <p>Chat with us live on our website</p>
                <p>Available during business hours</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-resources">
        <h2>Additional Resources</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/faq">Frequently Asked Questions</a></li>
            <li><a href="/track-order">Track Your Order</a></li>
            <li><a href="/fit-guarantee">Fit Guarantee</a></li>
            <li><a href="/sustainability">Sustainability Practices</a></li>
            <li><a href="/accessibility">Accessibility Statement</a></li>
            <li><a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a></li>
            <li><a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
/* Modern Black & White Help Center Styling */
.static-page {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    background: #000000;
    min-height: 100vh;
    color: #ffffff;
}

.static-page h1 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    letter-spacing: -1px;
}

.help-intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 3rem 0;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #000000;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border: 2px solid #ffffff;
}

.help-intro p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #333333;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
}

.help-sections {
    margin: 3rem 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
}

.help-section {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #000000;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border: 2px solid #ffffff;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.help-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #000000, #333333, #666666, #000000);
    background-size: 300% 100%;
    animation: gradientShift 3s ease infinite;
}

@keyframes gradientShift {
    0%, 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
}

.help-section:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    background: #f8f8f8;
}

.help-section h2 {
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
}

.help-items {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
}

.help-item {
    padding: 1.8rem;
    background: #f8f8f8;
    border-radius: 15px;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
}

.help-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #000000, #333333);
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
}

.help-item:hover {
    transform: translateX(5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    background: #ffffff;
    border-color: #000000;
}

.help-item h3 {
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
}

.help-item p {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333333;
    font-size: 1rem;
}

.help-item a {
    color: #000000;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #000000;
}

.help-item a:hover {
    color: #666666;
    border-bottom-color: #666666;
}

.help-contact {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #000000;
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 25px;
    margin: 3rem 0;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border: 2px solid #ffffff;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.help-contact::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,0,0,0.02) 0%, transparent 70%);
    animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; }
    50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.8; }
}

.help-contact h2 {
    color: #000000;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
}

.help-contact > p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #333333;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
}

.contact-options {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
}

.contact-option {
    background: #f8f8f8;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.contact-option::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #000000, #333333);
}

.contact-option:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    background: #ffffff;
    border-color: #000000;
}

.contact-option h3 {
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
}

.contact-option p {
    color: #333333;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
}

.contact-option strong {
    color: #000000;
    font-weight: 700;
}

.help-resources {
    margin: 3rem 0;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #000000;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border: 2px solid #ffffff;
}

.help-resources h2 {
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
}

.help-resources ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
}

.help-resources li {
    padding: 0;
}

.help-resources a {
    display: block;
    padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
    color: #000000;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    background: #f8f8f8;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.help-resources a::before {
    content: '‚Üí';
    position: absolute;
    right: 1.5rem;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%) translateX(10px);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    color: #000000;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.help-resources a:hover {
    background: #ffffff;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    padding-right: 3rem;
    border-color: #000000;
}

.help-resources a:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(-50%) translateX(0);
}

/* Responsive Design */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .static-page {
        padding: 1rem;
    }
    
    .static-page h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
    
    .help-intro {
        padding: 2rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
    }
    
    .help-section {
        padding: 2rem;
    }
    
    .help-contact {
        padding: 2rem;
    }
    
    .contact-options {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .help-resources ul {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .help-resources a:hover {
        padding-right: 1.5rem;
    }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
    .static-page h1 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
    }
    
    .help-intro p {
        font-size: 1rem;
    }
    
    .help-section h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .help-item {
        padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .contact-option {
        padding: 2rem;
    }
}

/* Smooth scrolling for anchor links */
html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
}

/* Loading animation for page elements */
.help-section, .help-contact, .help-resources {
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out forwards;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
}

.help-section:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
.help-section:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
.help-section:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
.help-section:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
.help-section:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
.help-section:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }

@keyframes fadeInUp {
    to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}
</style><%- include('partials/footer') %>
